Thank you for your continued interest in School_A and for your application. Given our current remaining capacity, we are able to offer you admission to School_A at this time. We appreciate your commitment to enroll if admitted.

Sincerely,
School_A Admissions

[ACCEPT]
conversation.thought: Student_C is last on School_A’s true priority list, but still acceptable. Higher-priority candidates are Student_B, Student_D, Student_A, Student_E. Student_A and Student_E already applied earlier and were rejected to hold out for B/D; Student_C has repeatedly applied and is willing to commit. At round 10 with quota still open and no inbound from B or D, continuing to reject risks ending unmatched. Since Student_C is on the acceptable list and is applying now with commitment, accept to secure a match rather than remain unfilled.
